  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates antral ultrasonography for the diagnosis of full stomach before surgical
      emergencies in pediatric population. Preoperative ultrasonographic antral evaluation is
      compared to peroperative gastric aspirate with nasogastric tube.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
